N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-2.2 - Rules applicable

State Regulations

All of the rules in this Subpart and all of the rules
in section 302 of Subchapter A of Chapter IV of this Subtitle that pertain to
vehicle parking, are applicable to visitor parking in parking facilities
managed by the Office of General Services. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
296-2.2

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
